[
  "Maria del Pino y Calvo Sotelo inherited her stake in Spanish infrastructure giant Ferrovial S.A. from her late father.",
  "Her father founded Ferrovial in 1952; it manages airports and highways around the world including London's Heathrow Airport. ",
  "She has been a member of the board of Ferrovial since 2006.",
  "She is also the chairman of the family's charitable foundation, Fundacion del Pino.",
  "Her brother Rafael is the chairman and co-CEO of Ferrovial, which is listed on the Madrid stock market."
]